%% F046 — console renders only real data: live selector, coverage, agent insights, settings, keys.
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Console (F018)
    participant API as norviq-api
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Loader as PolicyLoader (in-proc)

    Note over UI,API: cluster/namespace selector (replaces hardcoded CLUSTERS/NS_BY_CLUSTER)
    UI->>API: GET /api/v1/cluster-info (Bearer)
    API->>DB: distinct namespaces over policies+audit+agents
    DB-->>API: namespaces
    API-->>UI: {cluster_id, cluster_name, namespaces}  NRVQ-API-7080

    Note over UI,API: Dashboard posture gauge + category bars (replaces magic formulas)
    UI->>API: GET /coverage-by-category?namespace=
    API->>Loader: rego loaded for namespace
    API->>API: covered = mapped rule_ids present in rego (category_mapping.json)
    API-->>UI: {coverage_pct, categories[]}  NRVQ-API-7081

    Note over UI,API: Agent detail (replaces synthetic toolUsage/trustHistory)
    UI->>API: GET /agents/{id}/tool-usage + /trust-history?range=
    API->>DB: aggregate audit_log for the agent
    DB-->>API: rows
    API-->>UI: counts + per-day buckets  NRVQ-API-7082/7083

    Note over UI,API: Settings (replaces localStorage-only hardcoded defaults)
    UI->>API: GET /settings?namespace=
    API->>DB: NamespaceSettings override
    API-->>UI: effective = config defaults + override  NRVQ-API-7084
    UI->>API: PUT /settings (admin, validated)
    API->>DB: upsert override
    API-->>UI: saved  NRVQ-API-7085

    Note over UI,API: API keys (replaces stub) — secret shown once, only hash stored
    UI->>API: POST /keys (admin)
    API->>DB: insert ApiKey(hash, role, namespace)
    API-->>UI: {..., key: SECRET (once)}  NRVQ-API-7092
    UI->>API: GET request with Bearer nrvq_<key>
    API->>API: JWT invalid -> authenticate_api_key
    API->>DB: lookup by hash, not revoked -> principal  NRVQ-API-7090
